&lt;text text-anchor=&#39;middle&#39; x=&#39;168&#39; y=&#39;36&#39; fill=&#39;currentColor&#39; style=&#39;font-size:1em&#39;&gt;𝐯&lt;/text&gt;
&lt;text text-anchor=&#39;middle&#39; x=&#39;208&#39; y=&#39;132&#39; fill=&#39;currentColor&#39; style=&#39;font-size:1em&#39;&gt;𝐱&lt;/text&gt;
&lt;/g&gt;

